<h4 id="10-е°ҪйҮҸз”Ё-enumerate-еҸ–д»Ј-range">10. е°ҪйҮҸз”Ё enumerate еҸ–д»Ј range</h4>

<p>еңЁеҜ№еҲ—иЎЁиҝӣиЎҢиҝӯд»Јзҡ„ж—¶еҖҷпјҢйҖҡеёёиҝҳжғізҹҘйҒ“еҪ“еүҚе…ғзҙ еңЁеҲ—иЎЁдёӯзҡ„зҙўеј•гҖӮдёҖз§Қж–№ејҸдҪҝз”Ё range</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
<span class="c1"># дҪҝз”Ё range
</span><span class="n">flavor_list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'vanilla'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'chocolate'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'pecan'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'strawberry'</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">flavor_list</span><span class="p">)):</span>
    <span class="n">flavor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">flavor_list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"{0}:{1}"</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">flavor</span><span class="p">))</span>

<span class="s">'''Output:
1:vanilla
2:chocolate
3:pecan
4:strawberry
'''</span>

<span class="c1"># дҪҝз”ЁеҶ…зҪ®зҡ„ enumerate еҮҪж•°,иҫ“еҮәз»“жһңе’ҢдёҠйқўдёҖж ·
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">flavor</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">enumerate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">flavor_list</span><span class="p">):</span>
     <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"{0}:{1}"</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">flavor</span><span class="p">))</span>
     
<span class="c1"># иҝҳеҸҜд»ҘзӣҙжҺҘжҢҮе®ҡ enumerate еҮҪж•°ејҖе§Ӣи®Ўж•°ж—¶жүҖз”Ёзҡ„еҖј
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">flavor</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">enumerate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">flavor_list</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">):</span>
     <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"{0}:{1}"</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">flavor</span><span class="p">))</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>иҰҒзӮ№пјҡ
    <ul>
      <li>enumerate еҮҪж•°жҸҗдҫӣдәҶдёҖз§ҚзІҫз®Җзҡ„еҶҷжі•пјҢеҸҜд»ҘеңЁйҒҚеҺҶиҝӯд»ЈеҷЁж—¶иҺ·еҸ–жҜҸдёӘе…ғзҙ зҡ„зҙўеј•</li>
      <li>е°ҪйҮҸз”Ё enumerate жқҘж”№еҶҷйӮЈз§Қе°Ҷ range дёҺдёӢиЎЁи®ҝй—®зӣёз»“еҗҲзҡ„еәҸеҲ—йҒҚеҺҶд»Јз Ғ</li>
      <li>еҸҜд»Ҙз»ҷ enumerate жҸҗдҫӣз¬¬дәҢдёӘеҸӮж•°пјҢд»ҘжҢҮе®ҡејҖе§Ӣи®Ўж•°ж—¶жүҖз”Ёзҡ„еҖј(й»ҳи®Өдёә0)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4 id="11-з”Ё-zip-еҮҪж•°еҗҢж—¶йҒҚеҺҶиҝһдёӘиҝӯд»ЈеҷЁ">11. з”Ё zip еҮҪж•°еҗҢж—¶йҒҚеҺҶиҝһдёӘиҝӯд»ЈеҷЁ</h4>

<p>еҰӮжһңдёӨдёӘеҲ—иЎЁжңүзӣёдә’е…іиҒ”е…ізі»пјҢеҰӮжһңжғіе№іиЎҢзҡ„иҝӯд»ЈдёӨд»ҪеҲ—иЎЁпјҢеҰӮдёӢ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">names</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'Cecilia'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'Lise'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'Marie'</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">letters</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">n</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">names</span><span class="p">]</span>

<span class="n">longest_name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">None</span>
<span class="n">max_letters</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>

<span class="c1"># дҪҝз”Ё range жңҖеӮ»пјҢдёҚдёҠд»Јз ҒпјҢж¬Ўд№ӢдҪҝз”Ё enumerate иҝӯд»Ј
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">enumerate</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">names</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">letters</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">max_letters</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">longest_name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">name</span>
        <span class="n">max_letters</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">count</span>
        <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"{}-&gt;{}"</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">longest_name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">max_letters</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="c1">#Cecilia-&gt;7
</span>
<span class="c1"># дҪҝз”Ё zip иҝӣиЎҢе№іиЎҢиҝӯд»Ј
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">count</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">zip</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">names</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">letters</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">count</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">max_letters</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">longest_name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">name</span>
        <span class="n">max_letters</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">count</span>
        <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"{}-&gt;{}"</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">longest_name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">max_letters</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>жіЁж„ҸеҶ…зҪ®зҡ„ zip жңүдёӨдёӘй—®йўҳпјҡ
    <ul>
      <li>Python2дёӯзҡ„ zip е№¶дёҚжҳҜз”ҹжҲҗеҷЁ,иҖҢжҳҜдјҡжҠҠејҖеҸ‘иҖ…жүҖжҸҗдҫӣзҡ„йӮЈдәӣиҝӯд»ЈеҷЁпјҢйғҪе№іиЎҢзҡ„йҒҚеҺҶдёҖж¬ЎпјҢеңЁжӯӨиҝҮзЁӢдёӯпјҢе®ғдјҡжҠҠйӮЈдәӣиҝӯд»ЈеҷЁжүҖдә§з”ҹзҡ„еҖјжұҮиҒҡжҲҗе…ғзҘ–пјҢе№¶жҠҠйӮЈдәӣе…ғз»„жүҖжһ„жҲҗзҡ„еҲ—иЎЁе®Ңж•ҙең°иҝ”еӣһз»ҷи°ғз”ЁиҖ…гҖӮиҝҷеҸҜиғҪдјҡеҚ з”ЁеӨ§йҮҸеҶ…еӯҳеҜјиҮҙзЁӢеәҸеҙ©жәғгҖӮеңЁPython2дёӯз”ЁzipжқҘйҒҚеҺҶж•°жҚ®йҮҸйқһеёёеӨ§зҡ„иҝӯд»ЈеҷЁпјҢеә”иҜҘдҪҝз”ЁitertoolsеҶ…зҪ®жЁЎеқ—дёӯзҡ„ izip еҮҪж•°</li>
      <li>еҰӮжһңиҫ“е…Ҙзҡ„иҝӯд»ЈеҷЁй•ҝеәҰдёҚеҗҢпјҢйӮЈд№Ҳ zip дјҡиЎЁзҺ°еҮәжҜ”иҫғеҘҮжҖӘзҡ„иЎҢдёәгҖӮиӢҘдёҚиғҪзЎ®е®ҡzipжүҖе°ҒиЈ…зҡ„еҲ—иЎЁжҳҜеҗҰзӯүй•ҝпјҢеҲҷеҸҜиҖғиҷ‘ж”№з”Ё itertools еҶ…зҪ®жЁЎеқ—дёӯзҡ„ zip_longest еҮҪж•°(еңЁpython2дёӯеҸ«еҒҡ izip_longest)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>иҰҒзӮ№
    <ul>
      <li>еҶ…зҪ®зҡ„ zip еҮҪж•°еҸҜд»Ҙе№іиЎҢзҡ„йҒҚеҺҶеӨҡдёӘиҝӯд»ЈеҷЁ</li>
      <li>Python3дёӯзҡ„ zip зӣёеҪ“дәҺз”ҹжҲҗеҷЁпјҢдјҡеңЁйҒҚеҺҶиҝҮзЁӢдёӯйҖҗж¬Ўдә§з”ҹе…ғз»„пјҢиҖҢPython2дёӯзҡ„zipеҲҷжҳҜзӣҙжҺҘжҠҠиҝҷдәӣе…ғзҘ–е®Ңе…Ёз”ҹжҲҗеҘҪпјҢе№¶дёҖж¬ЎжҖ§ең°иҝ”еӣһж•ҙд»ҪеҲ—иЎЁ</li>
      <li>еҰӮжһңжҸҗдҫӣзҡ„иҝӯд»ЈеҷЁй•ҝеәҰдёҚзӯүпјҢйӮЈд№Ҳzipе°ұдјҡиҮӘеҠЁжҸҗеүҚз»Ҳжӯў</li>
      <li>itertools еҶ…зҪ®жЁЎеқ—дёӯзҡ„zip_lognest еҮҪж•°еҸҜд»Ҙе№іиЎҢең°йҒҚеҺҶеӨҡдёӘиҝӯд»ЈеҷЁпјҢиҖҢдёҚз”ЁеңЁд№Һе®ғд»¬зҡ„й•ҝеәҰжҳҜеҗҰзӣёзӯү</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4 id="12-дёҚиҰҒеңЁ-for-е’Ң-while-еҫӘзҺҜеҗҺйқўеҶҷ-else-еқ—">12. дёҚиҰҒеңЁ for е’Ң while еҫӘзҺҜеҗҺйқўеҶҷ else еқ—</h4>

<p>PythonжҸҗдҫӣдәҶдёҖз§ҚеҫҲеӨҡзј–зЁӢиҜӯиЁҖйғҪдёҚж”ҜжҢҒзҡ„еҠҹиғҪпјҢйӮЈе°ұжҳҜеҸҜд»ҘеңЁеҫӘзҺҜеҶ…йғЁзҡ„иҜӯеҸҘеқ—еҗҺйқўзӣҙжҺҘзј–еҶҷelseеқ—</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Loop {}'</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">))</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="k">break</span> <span class="c1"># еңЁеҫӘзҺҜйҮҢйқўз”Ёbreak иҜӯеҸҘжҸҗеүҚи·іеҮәпјҢдјҡеҜјиҮҙзЁӢеәҸдёҚжү§иЎҢelseеқ—
</span><span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Else block!'</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="s">'''
Loop 0
Loop 1
'''</span>

<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Loop {}'</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Else block!'</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
<span class="s">'''
Loop 0
Loop 1
Loop 2
Else block!
'''</span>

<span class="c1"># еҲқе§ӢеҫӘзҺҜжқЎд»¶дёәfalseзҡ„whileеҫӘзҺҜпјҢеҰӮжһңеҗҺйқўи·ҹзқҖelseеқ—пјҢйӮЈе®ғд№ҹдјҡз«ӢеҚіжү§иЎҢ
</span><span class="k">while</span> <span class="bp">False</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Never runs'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Whie Else block!'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">While</span> <span class="n">Else</span> <span class="n">block</span><span class="err">!</span>

<span class="c1"># еҰӮжһңforеҫӘзҺҜйҒҚеҺҶзҡ„еәҸеҲ—дёәз©әзҡ„пјҢдјҡз«ӢеҚіжү§иЎҢelseеқ—
</span><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="p">[]:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Nevers runs'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'For Else block!'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">For</span> <span class="n">Else</span> <span class="n">block</span><span class="err">!</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>иҰҒзӮ№
    <ul>
      <li>Pythonжңүз§Қзү№ж®ҠиҜӯжі•пјҢеҸҜеңЁforеҸҠwhile еҫӘзҺҜзҡ„еҶ…йғЁиҜӯеҸҘеқ—д№ӢеҗҺзҙ§и·ҹдёҖдёӘelseеқ—</li>
      <li>еҸӘжңүеҪ“ж•ҙдёӘеҫӘзҺҜдё»дҪ“йғҪжІЎйҒҮеҲ°breakиҜӯеҸҘж—¶пјҢеҫӘзҺҜеҗҺйқўзҡ„elseеқ—жүҚдјҡжү§иЎҢ</li>
      <li>дёҚиҰҒеңЁеҫӘзҺҜеҗҺйқўдҪҝз”Ёelseеқ—пјҢеӣ дёәиҝҷз§ҚеҶҷжі•ж—ўдёҚзӣҙи§ӮпјҢеҸҲе®№жҳ“еј•дәәиҜҜи§Ј</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h4 id="13-еҗҲзҗҶеҲ©з”Ё-tryexceptelsefinally-з»“жһ„дёӯзҡ„жҜҸдёӘд»Јз Ғеқ—">13. еҗҲзҗҶеҲ©з”Ё try/except/else/finally з»“жһ„дёӯзҡ„жҜҸдёӘд»Јз Ғеқ—</h4>

<p>ж··еҗҲдҪҝз”ЁзӨәдҫӢ: д»Һж–Үд»¶дёӯиҜ»еҸ–жҹҗйЎ№дәӢзү©зҡ„жҸҸиҝ°дҝЎжҒҜпјҢеӨ„зҗҶиҜҘдәӢеҠЎпјҢз„¶еҗҺе°ұең°жӣҙж–°иҜҘж–Үд»¶гҖӮ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">UNDEFINED</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">object</span><span class="p">()</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">divide_josn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">handler</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">path</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'r+'</span><span class="p">)</span>      <span class="c1"># May raise IOError
</span>    <span class="k">try</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">data</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">handler</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">read</span><span class="p">()</span>       <span class="c1"># May raise UnicodeDecodeError
</span>        <span class="n">op</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">json</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">loads</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">)</span>       <span class="c1"># May raise ValueError
</span>        <span class="n">value</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span>
            <span class="n">op</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'numerator'</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">/</span>
            <span class="n">op</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'denominator'</span><span class="p">])</span>      <span class="c1"># May raise ZeroDivisionError
</span>    <span class="k">except</span> <span class="nb">ZeroDivisionError</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">UNDEFINED</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">op</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'result'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">value</span>
        <span class="n">result</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">json</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">dumps</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">op</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">handle</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">seek</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">handle</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">write</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">result</span><span class="p">)</span>        <span class="c1"># May raise IOError
</span>        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">value</span>
    <span class="k">finally</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">handle</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">close</span><span class="p">()</span>              <span class="c1"># Always runs
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>иҰҒзӮ№
    <ul>
      <li>зү©зҗҶtryеқ—жҳҜеҗҰеҸ‘з”ҹејӮеёёпјҢйғҪеҸҜд»ҘеҲ©з”Ё try/finally еӨҚеҗҲиҜӯеҸҘдёӯзҡ„finally еқ—жқҘжү§иЎҢжё…зҗҶе·ҘдҪң</li>
      <li>elseеқ—еҸҜд»Ҙз”ЁжқҘзј©еҮҸtryеқ—дёӯзҡ„д»Јз ҒйҮҸпјҢе№¶жҠҠжІЎжңүеҸ‘з”ҹејӮеёёж—¶жүҖиҰҒжү§иЎҢзҡ„иҜӯеҸҘдёҺtry/except д»Јз Ғеқ—йҡ”ејҖ</li>
      <li>йЎәеҲ©иҝҗиЎҢtryеқ—еҗҺпјҢиӢҘжғіжҳҜжҹҗдәӣж“ҚдҪңиғҪеңЁfinallyеқ—зҡ„жё…зҗҶд»Јз Ғд№ӢеүҚжү§иЎҢпјҢеҲҷеҸҜе°Ҷиҝҷдәӣж“ҚдҪңеҶҷеҲ°elseеқ—дёӯ</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>
